{"tid":864346,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Tom and Jerry要拍真人動畫電影了！","createTime":"2018-10-16T06:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T10:21:08.000Z","uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9df8e334cc990cf01f723a06d12ab2bcc120b0a7","tid":864346,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"據外媒報導，華納正在與導演蒂姆&middot;斯托瑞商談拍攝《Tom and Jerry》的真人動畫混合電影。<br />\n<br />\n《Tom and Jerry》由MGM動畫工作室於1940年至1960年期間製作，該系列共有114部動畫短片，曾經贏得7座奧斯卡獎。<br />\n<br />\n故事主要講貓咪湯姆和老鼠傑瑞之間永無止境的戰爭，幾乎沒有台詞，妙趣橫生，受到各年齡層觀眾的喜愛。 1992年，系列推出了首部電影作品《Tom and Jerry Movie》。<br />\n<br />\n蒂姆&middot;斯托瑞代表作包括2014年喜劇《龍兄唬弟》，以及2016年的續集。他還執導過2005年的《神奇四俠》以及2007年的續集。<br />\n<br />\n除了《Tom and Jerry》之外，華納兄弟還在開發另一個自家IP。哈利&middot;波特電影製作人克里斯&middot;哥倫布將為一部《Scooby Doo》動畫電影擔任創作製作人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mtime.com/2018/10/16/1585152.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mtime.com%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2F1585152.html&d=EhBP80KDfqtSfCVNn%2BWU%2Fk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=38734d9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mtime.com/2018/10/16/1585152.html</a>"},{"pid":"4938c405f49df0874a89f3f58db5575a0484d3db","tid":864346,"uid":76632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"睇卡通時全程零對白。<br />\n<br />\n齋播背景音樂，同埋Tom不斷慘叫鳩叫都已經好有趣。"},{"pid":"2bc20d86cbd92b9f2616aabd9e3b06aecee734a8","tid":864346,"uid":207415,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/16/181916_1ca47d52983e7fad817cbd2ed96c0424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2F181916_1ca47d52983e7fad817cbd2ed96c0424.jpg&h=35cbcde4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eb6d57d2ffbe0ff945661c0d145166d7da4237f","tid":864346,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"